The truth is, the real purpose of education is simple and profound for every child :
• Control over the thoughts (peaceful mind without stress and anxiety)
• Control over the body (good health) 
• Skills to earn a living while maintaining a stress-free mind ( willingness to work,  not to chase the money)

Instead, the current system often pushes children toward unrealistic ambitions and an uncertain future with excessive digital dependence, drowning them in unnecessary information and endless screen time.

