"I really respect Geoffrey but it’s a shame he has such a strong political bias. 

When he lists Brexit and the election of Donald Trump as negative consequences of AI he alienates half of the people listening. Personally, I was in favor of both those electoral outcomes but I’m such a nerd for the topic that I can let it slide and listen to the rest of the conversation but I can guarantee you a lot of people immediately tune out. 

If your goal is to raise awareness and use your platform to reach as many people as possible, it would be much better to stay neutral on politics. I guess what I’m trying to say is don’t assume all your allies are on the left, there’s plenty of people on the right that are worried about the future of AI and would stand alongside you if you didn’t scare them off, Geoffrey.",AI,1
