"We formally request the full integration of China ROM features, visuals, and physics-based animations into Global builds. Our objective is to achieve complete UI parity and a seamless
(1)👻AI Interactive Companion 
is a highly customizable digital partner that stays on your home screen as a responsive widget, reflecting system health through its ""energy levels"" and battery-synced animations. It seamlessly integrates with existing widgets or stands alone, allowing you to change its entire theme and style to match your personal aesthetic while managing all on-device AI tasks
(2) 💻 The Office Kit introduces ""Origin Plugins,
 a deep integration layer that applies the full OriginOS design language and interactive skin over Windows and Linux for a premium, unified aesthetic. Crucially, it serves as a fail-safe; if Windows suffers a Blue Screen or system failure, the Kit instantly activates an integrated Android-based PC backup environment. This secondary OS hosts your synced files and active workspace, allowing you to continue your tasks without interruption even when the primary desktop OS fails
(3)🖌️ Super Icons (Icon Enlargement)
 OriginOS allows users to resize app icons using four different dimensional presets. To ensure a cohesive aesthetic, this ""Super Icon"" functionality is supported by all available Theme Icon Packs
(4) 🧊GridForge Seamless Block Architecture
GridForge allows users to visually merge enlarged icons and widgets into a single, gapless ""puzzle"" block, eliminating all dividing lines and padding. While the elements appear as one unified aesthetic unit, they maintain their independent functional performance for a cleaner, high-efficiency home screen experience
(5)🎨 AI Wallpapers
Use Little Blue and Gemini to generate art from text prompts or transform existing photos into wallpapers
(6)🫆 Custom fingerprint 
This feature allows users to personalize their fingerprint scanner by using custom PNG images or photos instead of standard emojis. It offers full creative freedom to replace the default biometric icon with any transparent graphic or personal image for a truly unique lock screen experience
(7)🎭Deep system theming 
implements adaptive custom designs that reshape the entire UI, from Control Center toggles to system menus. Rather than simple color shifts, it integrates unique textures like glassmorphism to ensure the entire interface functions as a singular, cohesive masterpiece
(8)🇨🇳 OriginOS China Features (Requesting for Global)
Visual Identity & Status Bar: The specific ""Blackish Look"" status bar found in OriginOS 6 (China)
Icon & Widget Library Complete port of all exclusive Icon Styles, Dynamic Widgets,and the ""App Suggestions Kit
(9)Full Gesture Customization
Implement the advanced gesture control system from OriginOS (China). This should allow users to fully customize navigation triggers, swipe areas, and gesture sensitivity to match the fluidity of the Chinese ROM
(10) Granular Control Center Customization
Enable full customization for every individual tile within the Control Center. Users should be able to resize, rearrange, and reshape each toggle to match the personalized aesthetic of the rest of the OS
(11) Advanced Blur Control Engine
 Introduce a dedicated setting to manage system-wide blur effects. This should include a Blur Intensity Slider and three distinct presets: Liquid Glass (high transparency/fluid look), Light Blur (subtle depth), and Frosted Glass (heavy/matte texture). Additionally, provide independent blur controls for the Control Center and Widgets to allow for a customized aesthetic across different UI layers
(12) Smart Widget Stacks: 
Allow users to stack multiple widgets of the same size on top of each other. Users can swipe through them manually or let the system rotate them based on time or usage patterns, saving home screen space while maintaining functionality
(13) Physics-Based Interaction Engine:
 Upgrade the animation engine to include ""Elastic Physics."" This means when you pull a menu or swipe a card, the UI should have a natural bounce and stretch (inertia) that reacts to the speed of your finger, making the software feel like a physical object rather than digital code
(14) Advanced Desktop Mode Integration:
 Implement a dedicated ""Desktop Mode"" similar to Samsung DeX, allowing the smartphone to transform into a full desktop interface when connected to an external monitor or PC. This should include a taskbar, multi-window support, and full mouse/keyboard optimization, moving beyond simple screen mirroring to provide a true professional workstation experience 
(15)The Advanced Procedural Widget 
Engine allows for deep, KWGT-style customization of layers and variables directly within the system UI. It features a Physics-Based Blur Engine for real-time frosted glass effects and Layered Parallax Animations that ensure every interaction feels fluid and high-end
16.🕰️ Dynamic Standby Landscape Mode: Transforms the idle screen into a premium dashboard when placed horizontally. It features customizable dual-pane widgets for clocks, weather, and music, combined with battery-efficient, motion-responsive animations for a high-end desk accessory feel",Tech,0
